# Fylgja powers

**Roots:** `WILLOW_FYLGJA_ROOT` if set, else `~/github/willow-2.0/willow/fylgja`.

1. `Read` `{ROOT}/powers/registry.json` (catalog only).
2. Pick the single best `powers[].id` by `description` for the user task. **Bounded initiative** that must stay off default branch until ratified merge → prefer **`overseer`**. Willow MCP/KB/Grove/SOIL work with no tighter fit → prefer **`agent-rails`**.
3. `Read` `{ROOT}/powers/{file}` for that entry — **one** power body per turn unless the user asks for more.
4. If that power points you at longer prose, `Read` `{ROOT}/skills/<name>.md` **only then**.

Do **not** mirror verbose “load every skill at 1% probability” packs. User instructions override this rule.

Full surface map: `{ROOT}/powers/SURFACES.md`.
